<p>I have an almost moral dislike for the four-wheeled suitcase. Bear with me here. Before 1972, luggage had no wheels. Then, Bernard Sadow <a href="https://image-ppubs.uspto.gov/dirsearch-public/print/downloadPdf/3653474" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">patented</a> this design with four small wheels and a strap:</p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F09763b8f-ccd5-4f0d-8ea0-2558ccc95be1_980x1324.png" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/VpYewhOjS_lXaXK6_ 424w, https://reader.miniflux. 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/enl7aLt0O9iIykaEfOs_sT_6QZNa5BCIT_m-9L4BE8M=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xMjcyLGNfbGltaXQsZl93ZWJwLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGMDk3NjNiOGYtY2NkNS00ZjBkLThlYTAtMjU1OGNjYzk1YmUxXzk4MHgxMzI0LnBuZw== 1272w, https://reader.miniflux. 1456w" sizes="100vw"/><img src="https://reader.miniflux." width="404" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/pPdsKUR-I-Xho1Xy3dmlFCFc7y--spYxTbs8ni854N0=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX2F1dG8scV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkYwOTc2M2I4Zi1jY2Q1LTRmMGQtOGVhMC0yNTU4Y2NjOTViZTFfOTgweDEzMjQucG5n 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/4jBu1YiajZ5vo- 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/hRGfk9KY11D4_Ya-ks-o_qb1Paqa-XrPsJH_KqpTfcE=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xMjcyLGNfbGltaXQsZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGMDk3NjNiOGYtY2NkNS00ZjBkLTh